     that `:- module(_modulename_,_exports_)' is equivalent to `:-
     module(_modulename_,_exports_,[default])' If you do not want
     these predicates/features loaded for a given file (in order to
     make the executable smaller) you can ask for this explicitly
     using `:- module(_modulename_,_exports_,[])' or in a user file
     `:- use_package([])'.

